otherFacts.name: Interior Features
otherFacts.value: Main Bedroom Bath, Country Kitchen, Great Room, Common Rec Room

data.description: Beautiful family home in a quiet subdivision! Wooded lot!  The home was built in 2015, and the lower level was finished in 2018. This home features 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. The main level has a large entry way leading to an open concept living room, kitchen, and dining area. The upper level holds 2 bedrooms, master bedroom and walk in closet, and 2 bathrooms. On the lower level you will find a large living room, a bedroom, bathroom, and laundry room. You can get into the crawl space from the lower level. You can also access the lower level through the garage. The garage is a large two car garage at 26x28 feet. This home would be perfect for a family looking for some nice open space in a quiet subdivision!
